Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來沒有精神呢
