Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於諾艾爾的事情  別對我們有所隱瞞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
