Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿饅頭來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:11:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個朋友想介紹給你們認識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
