Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  關於戶川同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是指轉學的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音是我們重要的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望遠鏡由我來帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後來我店裡拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望遠鏡交給我來搬吧  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  求求妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們再談一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想就這樣和妳告別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從諾艾爾那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現願望的話  諾艾爾就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是回到父親那裡住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了諾艾爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望大家一起無論何時都能充滿歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再失去任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到底要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  這種事不需要去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們沒有天文臺的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被你拉進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我消失  就能讓諾艾爾留下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就沒問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音覺得這樣就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也對大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼和我也是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥太狡猾了  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:15:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾無論如何都想實現乃乃香的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為…被我們召喚而來到這座小鎮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始確實這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到大家的時候就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為大家的願望非常非常得純潔美好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都歡笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時心都相連著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是件非常非常美好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  諾艾爾想看到歡笑著的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  這已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事做的話就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問問她關於汐音的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的汐音一定有什麼隱情
