Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和汐音談一談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊回乃乃香那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  今天已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  妳這幾天都在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我們好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於諾艾爾的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去拿望遠鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能歡笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓諾艾爾消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是戶川也可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要五人不聚在一起就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要我離開你們就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是讓一直因為飛碟給大家添麻煩的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以交給笨蛋柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢  笨蛋湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊…太？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音都告訴你們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…這種事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾那天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天文臺的上空  聽見了大家的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚飛碟的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚諾艾爾的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以諾艾爾才能和大家相見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與乃乃香初次相遇的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就明白了  呼喚我的人是乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乃乃香一起共度時光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我唱好聽的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香做的飯特別好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  小春  湊太  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都非常溫柔  讓人暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾笑得非常非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在很清楚地知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾想看到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  汐音  小春  柚季還有湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠一起歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為諾艾爾最喜歡大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾必須要和大家分別
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  天體的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
